metadata.title: Become a Project Partner - Inteli - Institute of Technology and Leadership

content_blocks.text: Inteli Project Partners
Benefits of being a partner
As our partner, you can submit initiatives for different project models according to the modules available for student learning. The fruits of this partnership are diverse:
Available public notices

Our Call for Projects is the way we let the market know what projects are available. Below you can see our portfolio of projects that we carry out year after year and through which we receive applications for initiatives from companies, NGOs and government institutions with their business challenges.

The initiatives submitted are evaluated and selected by the Project Office and follow the rules of ourcall for proposals. Once their initiative has been selected, the partner will sign apartnershipagreement.

The project modules are cyclical and are carried out annually in the corresponding quarters, according to the portfolio below. Digital game Decentralized software using blockchain Digital distributed processing system Process and system automation High-performance solution using graphs Deep learning system applied to computer vision Resilient digital system with quality as a software asset Hyperconnectivity for Smart Cities Management Data Control Reports and Dashboards Financial modeling and valuation Web application Mobile robotics and computer vision Combinatorial optimization and operational research Digital platform based on service-oriented architecture Application based on Natural Language Processing Agile software production treadmill Behavioral Analysis of Digital Interface Users Application of artificial neural networks in reinforcement learning Hyperscalable applications Logic for prediction with artificial intelligence Management Systems and Corporate Governance Predictive modeling in business applications using deep learning Predictive maintenance system with AI and cloud architecture Scalable application in distributed systems Edge computing system Data architecture and governance aligned with corporate strategy Natural language processing system with generative AI Natural language processing in text, video and audio IoT solution IDE for sensory device accessibility Autonomous service robot with generative AI Secure and fault-tolerant digital architecture Big Data Integration, Management and Analysis

The delivery to be made by the student groups consists of a prototype that incorporates the functionalities/requirements defined for the web application in question, in line with the learning content presented and agreed with the selected Market Partner via the Project Office. The prototypes developed are made available for use by the partner one month after the end of the module.Check out theprototypesalready made in this module.
